title: Ar Tonelico 1&2 OSTs
description:
Music from the Ar Tonelico 1&2 RPGs to PS2. These are the full OSTs, as far as I can tell, but there's a lot of music that didn't make it onto the discs.

Which is unfortunate. Never the less, all the Hymns seem to be included, and that's the main thing. Track names are in Japanese.

The second game is awesome, by the way. Haven't played the first one.


...Also, is there any chance somebody's got a spare demonoid invite code lying around?

(Lastly, my max up speed is about 55kb/s, so shush with the whining.)
